text: Santo Tomás is a corregimiento in Alanje District, Chiriquí Province, Panama. It has a land area of and had a population of 1,259 as of 2010, giving it a population density of . Its population as of 1990 was 721; its population as of 2000 was 840. ==References== Category:Corregimientos of Chiriquí Province
